# https://w3id.org/narn/social/wasHeldCaptiveIn
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/wasHeldCaptiveIn> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/narn/social/wasHeldCaptiveIn> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/narn/social/livedIn> .
